description: All things Alien! 添加新的敌人、增强食人虫及喷吐虫巢穴。给需要更多挑战的你。该Mod是自然演化mod的其中之一，不过也能单独使用。访问主页以了解更多信息。
description_original: All things Alien! Adds new Enemies and updates to Biter/Spitters Spawners. If you want a more of a challenge than what Vinalla can offer you... Part of the N.E. Mods, but can be used as Standalone. Please visit home page for more details.
